ality":"Massage, Craniosacral","modalities":["Massage","Craniosacral"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Therapeutic Massage and Bodywork\nUnique Mind-Body-Spirit Vibroacoustic Massage | Skilled, Compassionate, Effective Care \nAdvanced Training and Specialization in Chest,  Breast, and Post-Mastectomy Massage\nSupporting Women to Heal, Recover & Thrive","location":"Keaau","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:57:39.919944+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"2273a91f-d8a9-4b3e-bfbc-c5263f722e57","name":"Tina Pliura-Mohr","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/practitioners/1775026409441-7exg3gazo.webp","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage, Craniosacral","modalities":["Massage","Craniosacral"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Tina is a highly skilled practitioner with over 35 years of experience specializing in injury care and restorative bodywork. Caring, competent and compassionate, Tina offers a variety of foundational and advanced bodywork modalities as a true healer.","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:57:39.217838+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"fd772e97-a9c1-4e2e-ad5a-1fa9f2da378c","name":"Tomi Knutson","image":"https://www.tomiknutson.com/uploads/2/3/3/9/2339187/published/img-8123.jpeg?1745054030","type":"practitioner","modality":"Craniosacral, Massage, Family Constellation","modalities":["Craniosacral","Massage","Family Constellation"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Hello, my name is Tomi Knutson and I am an LMT and Integrative practitioner specializing in Adult and Pediatric Craniosacral Therapy, Manual Lymph Drainage, and Family Constellation Work. In 2021, a long-held dream of mine came true when I moved to the Big Island of Hawaii from Oakland, CA. I now practice here in